    "By combining MarioGPT with the Novelty Search algorithm [150], an open-ended level generation process was formed.",
    "Novelty search can continually discover levels with diverse structures and gameplay styles.2) Text-to-image Generation: In this type of task, when using LLMs like Stable Diffusion [151] to generate photorealistic images, it is necessary to optimize the input text prompts and model parameters in order to achieve better performance.",
